<main>
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row">
			
		</div>
		<div class="row">
			
			<div class="col s12 m8 offset-m2 l6 offset-l3">
				<p>Here's the profile we found:</p>
		        <div class="card-panel grey lighten-5 z-depth-1">
		          <div class="row valign-wrapper">
		            <div class="col s2">
		              <img src="<%= @profile_pic_url %>" alt="" class="circle responsive-img">
		            </div>
		            <div class="col s10">
		              <span class="black-text">
		                <strong><%= @name %></strong>
		              </span>
		              <br>
		              <span class="black-text">
		                <%= @bio %>
		              </span>
		            </div>
		          </div>
		        </div>
      		</div> 
		</div>
		<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/2.1.4/Chart.min.js"></script>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col s12 m8 offset-m2 l6 offset-l3">
				<p>Here's the radar chart. Each axis measures one of the <%= link_to 'Big Five personality traits', 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Big_Five_personality_traits' %>. </p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="s12">
				<canvas id="personalityChart"></canvas>
			</div>
			<div class="col s12 m8 offset-m2 l6 offset-l3">
				<p>The test shop is no longer active, so products are no longer being recommended, but we can still analyse personalities.</p>

				<p>If you'd like to integrate this to your shop, contact me through the Github page linked in the footer. You can also visit it for the code. </p>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<script type="text/javascript">
			var ctx = document.getElementById('personalityChart').getContext('2d')
			var personalityChart = new Chart(ctx, {
			  type: 'radar',
			  data: {
			    labels: ['Openness', 'Extraversion', 'Emotional Range', 'Conscientiousness', 'Agreeableness'],
			    fontSize: "18",
			    datasets: [{
		          pointHighlightFill : "gray",
			      label: 'Percentile',

			      data: ["<%= @analysis["personality"][0]["percentile"] * 100 %>",
			      		 "<%= @analysis["personality"][1]["percentile"] * 100 %>",
			      		 "<%= @analysis["personality"][2]["percentile"] * 100 %>",
			      		 "<%= @analysis["personality"][3]["percentile"] * 100 %>",
			      		 "<%= @analysis["personality"][4]["percentile"] * 100 %>"
			      		],
			      backgroundColor: "rgba(186, 53, 40, 0.4)",

			    }]
			  },
			  options: { 
		        legend: {
		            labels: {
		                fontColor: "gray" 
		                              
		            }
		        },

		        scale: {
		        	gridLines: {
		        		color: "gray"
		        		
		        	},

		        	pointLabels: {
		            backgroundColor: "gray"
		           
		          }
		        },

		        responsive: true


		    }
			});
			Chart.defaults.global.defaultFontColor = 'gray';



		</script>
		<div class="line"></div>

		<div class="product-content">
		<div style="color: white">
			
		</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</main>


